Function Reference/update blog public « WordPress Codex
-----------

Update this blog's 'public' setting in the global blogs table.

Public blogs have a setting of 1, private blogs are 0.

Usage
-----

` <?php update_blog_public( $old_value, $value ); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$old_value` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*)
    Default: *None*

 `$value` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The new public value
    Default: *None*

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(bool)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   

Source File
-----------

`update_blog_public()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

